author: @kelia.chunjia
text:
STREAMING INSTRUCTIONS & SEQUENCE:

1. Instructions (these might help increase the views and prevent views freeze):

- Volume should be >50 (not very important actually:))

- MUST MUST MUST SEARCH FOR EVERY MVs, don't watch the playlist that YouTube recommends.

- Only exit the videos after SM's logo disappear at the end.

- Change the channel after watched 3 MVs (whatever that is not from the SM channel) for some mins.

- Don't forget to LIKE & COMMENT.

- You can skip the ads but watch them sometimes.

- You can pause or rewind the videos but please DON'T FAST FORWARD it.

- You can stream on different webs but the account must be different.



2. Sequence (I only recommend this but you can change the order, it's up to you:)) 

◇ take a break between dot rows below◇

• Tempo -> Growl -> Call me baby.

[[Change the channel for 5 mins, you can watch EXO's reality shows cut]]

• Let's love (Suho) -> Candy (Baekhyun) -> That's okay (D.O).

[[Change channel! The Eve dance practice?]]

• Overdose -> Love shot -> Monster

[[Take a break]]

• Ko Ko Pop -> Obsession -> You (Xiumin)

[[Change the channel or take a break]]

• Mmmh (Kai) -> Lotto -> Amusement Park (Baekhyun)

[[Changeeeee]]

• Sing for you -> Universe -> Power.

[[Breakk]]

• Lit (Lay) -> Hello (Chen) -> Lucky

[[you know what to do :))))]]

• For Life -> Love me right -> Dinner (Suho) 

[[Watch the dance practice]]

• UN village (Baekhuyn) -> Wolf -> 1 Billion Views.

[[.....]]

• What a life -> Hey Mama! -> Electric Kiss

[[Change channel]]

• ......you can add more by yourself......

■ There are a lot MVs as EXO has some other sub-units, so I can't list down everything. You can reply to this with more MVs that we should stream ■

■ Let's make some surprise for EXO on their anniversary, guyss ■
